#~ "documents you are working on. This feature can be disabled in the <link "
#~ "linkend=\"config-dialog-treeview\">Documents</link> page of the "
#~ "configuration dialog."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Dokumentlistan visar normalt historiken genom att skugga posterna för de "
